otential candidate nuclei include 153Eu, 161Dy, 221Fr, 223Fr,\n223Ra, 223Rn, 225Ac, 227Ac, 229Th, 229Pa, 233U and 235U. We subsequently\nconsider molecules containing these nuclei (EuO, EuN+, RaF, AcO, AcN+, AcF+,\nThO and ThF+).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Apr 2022 07:51:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 02:47:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
